### 带过滤和重排的查询
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "平台能力？",
  "top_k": 3,
  "mode": "rag",
  "rerank": true,
  "filters": {
    "tenant_id": "tenant-001",
    "tags": ["platform", "features"]
  }
}

